                            <small class="text-secondary">Professional Trader</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Slide 2 -->
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="testimonial-card mx-auto p-5">
                            <div class="quote-icon top-icon">❝</div>
                            <p class="lead mb-4">
                                “Clean UI, simple budgeting, and powerful insights. I finally understand where my money
                                goes.”
                            </p>
                            <div class="quote-icon bottom-icon">❞</div>
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3 mb-0">Aisha M</h6>
                            <small class="text-secondary">Investor</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Slide 3 -->
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="testimonial-card mx-auto p-5">
                            <div class="quote-icon top-icon">❝</div>
                            <p class="lead mb-4">
                                “The best finance tool I've used. Tracking, goals, and clarity in one place.”
                            </p>
                            <div class="quote-icon bottom-icon">❞</div>
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3 mb-0">Daniel O</h6>
                            <small class="text-secondary">Entrepreneur</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Controls -->
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev custom-nav" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonialCarousel"
                        data-bs-slide="prev">
                        ‹
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next custom-nav" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonialCarousel"
                        data-bs-slide="next">
                        ›
